nl.vrom.roo.validator.core.validation

Class ValidationFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.vrom.roo.gmlgeox.validation.ValidationFactory

  • public final class ValidationFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory to instantiate validations. The intention of this factory is to make is possible to be able to configure all Validations within a Validator
